## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/smallvectortemplatebase">SmallVectorTemplateBase</a>&lt;TriviallyCopyable = true&gt; - This is where we put method implementations that are designed to work with trivially copyable T&#39;s.

This allows using memcpy in place of copy/move construction and skipping destruction.

Definition at line 475 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/smallvector-h">SmallVector.h</a>.
